query.text:
pageViews
| where timestamp  between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| extend LegalEntity            = toupper(tostring( customDimensions.LegalEntity))
    ,   ExecutionMode           = customDimensions.ExecutionMode
    ,   BatchJobId              = customDimensions.BatchJobId
    ,   CallStack               = customDimensions.CallStack
    , FormInstanceId = customDimensions.FormInstanceId
    , FormEvent = customDimensions.FormEvent
| where FormInstanceId <> ''
| where _formName =='' or name == _formName
| project ["Timestamp"]             = timestamp
        , ["Name"]          = name
        , ["Session ID"]            = session_Id
        , ["User ID"]               = tostring(user_Id)
        , ["Legal Entity"]          = LegalEntity
        , ["Execution Mode"]        = tostring(ExecutionMode)
        , CallStack 
        , ["Client Type"]        = client_Type
        , ["Client City"]           = client_City
        , ["Client Country"]        = client_CountryOrRegion
        , ["Form Event"] = FormEvent
        , ["Form Instance Id"] = tostring( FormInstanceId)
| summarize ["Opening time (sec)"] = datetime_diff('second',max(Timestamp),min(Timestamp)), ["Last execution"] = max(Timestamp), ["User ID"] = any(["User ID"]) by Name,  ["Form Instance Id"]
|order by ['Opening time (sec)'] desc , ['Last execution'] desc 
| limit 100

tiles.title: Form interactions by name (top 100)
tiles.description: Note: the "Interaction difference" column can be used to identify forms that never complete the initialization.

query.text:
pageViews
| where timestamp  between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| extend LegalEntity            = toupper(tostring( customDimensions.LegalEntity))
    ,   ExecutionMode           = customDimensions.ExecutionMode
    ,   BatchJobId              = customDimensions.BatchJobId
    ,   CallStack               = customDimensions.CallStack
    , FormInstanceId = customDimensions.FormInstanceId
    , FormEvent = customDimensions.FormEvent
| where FormInstanceId <> ''
| where _formName =='' or name == _formName
| project ["Timestamp"]             = timestamp
        , ["Name"]          = name
        , ["Session ID"]            = session_Id
        , ["User ID"]               = user_Id
        , ["Legal Entity"]          = tostring( LegalEntity)
        , ["Execution Mode"]        = tostring(ExecutionMode)
        , CallStack 
        , ["Client Type"]        = client_Type
        , ["Client City"]           = client_City
        , ["Client Country"]        = client_CountryOrRegion
        , ["Form Event"] = tostring( FormEvent)
        , ["Form Instance Id"] = tostring( FormInstanceId)
| summarize Interactions = countif(['Form Event'] == 'onFormInit') , ["Interactions difference (init vs open complete)"] = countif(['Form Event'] == 'onFormInit') - countif(['Form Event'] == 'onFormRunCompleted'), ["Last Interaction"]= max( ["Timestamp"] )  by Name, ['Legal Entity']
| order by Interactions desc , ['Last Interaction'] desc
|limit 100
